data.text:
Owner John W. Galbreath, right, pats Chateaugay in winner's circle at Aqueduct Race Track in New York June 8, 1963 after the three-year-old won the 95th running of the Belmont Stakes. Jockey Braulio Baeza sits astride his mount. Handler is at left. (AP Photo)
